{"tid":2309388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國料本週通過阻中企上市法 中國氣炸：政治打壓！","createTime":"2020-12-02T13:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T14:44:26.000Z","uid":337052,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f52a967f4ae0b3e97b31f62ba9e209c56a9699d5","tid":2309388,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:35:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">阻中企赴美掛牌上市法案 美眾議院料本週通過</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/12/02 21:16<br />\n<br />\n（中央社華盛頓/香港2日綜合外電報導）<span class=\"red\">美國國會幕僚透露，聯邦眾議院本週料將通過一項法案，阻止中國企業在美國證券交易所掛牌上市，除非中企遵守美國的審計標準。</span><br />\n<br />\n這項法案將給中國電商巨擘阿里巴巴、拼多多，以及石油鉅子中國石油天然氣公司等3年的時間，遵循美國法律規定，否則將被踢出美國證券市場。<br />\n<br />\n業界人士表示，美國審查趨嚴也可能讓中國其它企業對赴美掛牌卻步不前。這類掛牌今年創下6年新高。<br />\n<br />\n眾院訂於今天傍晚投票表決「外國公司問責法案」（The Holding Foreign Companies Accountable Act）。其中規定若任何外國企業連續3年不配合「美國上市公司會計監督管理委員會」（U.S. Public Company Accounting Oversight Board）審查，將禁止這家企業的證券在任何美國證券交易所掛牌交易。<br />\n<br />\n國會幕僚表示，這項法案獲兩黨支持。對中國企業和貿易行徑採取更強硬路線的法案通常能在國會過關。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">中國外交部發言人華春瑩今天說：「這再次表明美國對中國的公司採取了歧視性的政策，對中國企業進行政治打壓。」</span>（譯者：劉淑琴/核稿：林治平）1091202<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202012020378.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202012020378.aspx&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOTsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=4bfd7c36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202012020378.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"e424e37f92dc3fe9ede50068704e10617b369d60","tid":2309388,"uid":310700,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nfr1Gtn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfr1Gtn.png&h=39caac0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2a0b6d4ac51ae7aadda9b4ee34c1a90f5379182","tid":2309388,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>燒春雞</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51dddd1a0beca17ce938bc128da0c9f65bd205e","tid":2309388,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390324f90aa77bab3d94f6b382afce0e481d31c1","tid":2309388,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:37:05.000Z","msg":"黐孖筋到底幾時先至派兵解放香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1c2230212047c553a1fc9708067d3bb8cddef1","tid":2309388,"uid":104845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:38:49.000Z","msg":"又搬石頭砸自己的腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f497efe8e6cdec62122329f14c5efb311cab768","tid":2309388,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:40:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美國將限制中企在美上市？外交部：反對政治打壓</span></strong><br />\n來源：<span class=\"red\">人民日報客戶端</span><br />\n<br />\n2020-12-02 16:34<br />\n<br />\n在2日舉行的外交部例行記者會上，有記者提問：據報導，美國眾議院本周可能會通過關於限制中國公司在美上市的議案。你對此有何評論？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">外交部發言人華春瑩回答：&zwnj;&zwnj;我想你剛才提到的&zwnj;&zwnj;這個&zwnj;&zwnj;問題&zwnj;&zwnj;再次的表明，美國對中國的公司採取了歧視性的政策，是對中國企業進行政治打壓。</span><br />\n<br />\n至於你提到的美國眾議院要表決外國公司&zwnj;&zwnj;問責法案這個具體的問題，你可以向主管部門詢問。<br />\n<br />\n我可以原則性地再跟你強調一下，&zwnj;&zwnj;在資本市場已經高度全球化的今天，有關各方開誠佈公地加強跨境監管合作，就保護投資者合法權益等議題來加強對話和合作才是解決問題的正道。<br />\n<br />\n&zwnj;&zwnj;我們堅決反對將證券監管政治化的做法。 &zwnj;&zwnj;我們希望美方&zwnj;&zwnj;能夠為外國的企業在美國投資和經營提供公平公正的環境，而不是想方設法設置層層&zwnj;&zwnj;障礙。 &zwnj;<br />\n<br />\n舉報我也說兩句責編：張燕萍"},{"pid":"c3fe3fd6db8f01b19bbd04026d894c2dc38b0bdf","tid":2309388,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2a0b6d4ac51ae7aadda9b4ee34c1a90f5379182","tid":2309388,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>燒春雞</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/11/30/phpmLt4pO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F11%2F30%2FphpmLt4pO.jpg&h=fb9b5d0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14e0ee3b4c9557da5f661691ae68a39a4c0d6b94","tid":2309388,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:51:34.000Z","msg":"仲畀夠三年時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059b014f999303fab60503361600a765e46c8d6a","tid":2309388,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14e0ee3b4c9557da5f661691ae68a39a4c0d6b94","tid":2309388,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:51:34.000Z","msg":"仲畀夠三年時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:53:22.000Z","msg":"應該在1年內"},{"pid":"a3e45c4f940efaea405b28e81bf0056c632041bc","tid":2309388,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20201202/800x600_666342286781.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F10